{"tid":2458189,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"721 第 20 個月　市民讀報紀念：點都要有人堅持","createTime":"2021-03-23T08:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T09:53:05.000Z","uid":261647,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed175487df17a312fb26d60e0944960d604392f8","tid":2458189,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:40:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/4000079900077600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F4000079900077600&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97e9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=0932abf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/4000079900077600</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSiZ92U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSiZ92U.png&h=c9adb41a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n【721 第 20 個月　市民讀報紀念：點都要有人堅持】<br />\n<br />\n今日是元朗 7.21 事件第 20 個月，元朗站地下連儂牆位置有數十名警員戒備。周先生到場舉起「伍健偉消失了」的紙牌，一度離開後，又重回現場「讀報」，報紙上貼著「毋忘 7.21」的文宣，在場只有他一名巿民在場逗留，「其他人放棄都好啦，點都要有人堅持。」<br />\n<br />\n他透露，自己每星期都會兩三次到場貼文宣，每次貼完就會迅速離開，避免有「藍絲」報警。他說，每晚貼過後，翌日早上很快就會被人撕走。他又曾被警員「點相」，截查近一小時才獲放行，但他說會繼續做能力範圍內的事，「比起啲人流亡、坐監、俾人政治逼害，我呢啲好小事，做到就做啦。」"},{"pid":"938b84d343b5e3df5e9d643e6f092fd5b7ee862e","tid":2458189,"uid":133033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T09:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}